Sean Patrick Thomas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sean_Patrick_Thomas 0 Sean Patrick Thomas (born December 17, 1970) is an American actor. He is known for his co-starring role in the 2001 film Save the Last Dance, as well as his television role as Detective Temple Page in The District.
